re_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/b7c35f44646fa531e3ddb2bbd21e9202.poster.avif?t=1715870970\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/b7c35f44646fa531e3ddb2bbd21e9202.webm?t=1715870970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/b7c35f44646fa531e3ddb2bbd21e9202.mp4?t=1715870970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>No longer limited by table size, you have an infinite area to build on. Place the blocks on the studs on the ground.<br><br><strong>Decorations</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/6bde939ca1ac6e6b88e1f806132395da.poster.avif?t=1715870970\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/6bde939ca1ac6e6b88e1f806132395da.webm?t=1715870970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/6bde939ca1ac6e6b88e1f806132395da.mp4?t=1715870970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Decorate your room with your creations<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br>- 300+ of different blocks<br>- 50+ materials<br>- 4 game modes<br>- 1000+ of community builds<br><br>Join our official Discord for more fun outside the game!",
